---
// AstroImage.astro
---

<img src="../src/images/astro.svg" alt="Astro" class="astro-image" />

<style>
  .astro-image {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    right: 0;
    max-height: 100vh;
    width: auto;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .astro-image {
      max-width: 100%;
      max-height: 50vh;
    }
  }
</style>
